This paper deals with Natural Language Processing (NLP) and specifically with Neural Relation Extraction (NRE), which falls under the category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques such as word embeddings and data augmentation, which are commonly used in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) research. The paper also touches upon the topic of bias in machine learning, which is a growing area of research in Social and Information Sciences (cs.SI) and Cybersecurity (cs.CY).
